WEBVTT

00:00:01.167 --> 00:00:02.474
Thank you.

00:00:02.474 --> 00:00:03.983
I have only got 18 minutes

00:00:03.983 --> 00:00:06.832
to explain something 
that lasts for hours and days,

00:00:06.832 --> 00:00:09.102
so I'd better get started.

00:00:09.102 --> 00:00:13.959
Let's start with a clip
from Al Jazeera's Listening Post.

00:00:14.649 --> 00:00:18.496
Richard Gizbert: Norway is a country that 
gets relatively little media coverage.

00:00:18.496 --> 00:00:21.487
Even the elections this past week
passed without much drama.

00:00:21.487 --> 00:00:24.145
And that's the Norwegian
media in a nutshell:

00:00:24.145 --> 00:00:25.622
not much drama.

00:00:25.622 --> 00:00:26.959
A few years back,

00:00:26.959 --> 00:00:29.416
Norway's public TV channel NRK

00:00:29.416 --> 00:00:33.593
decided to broadcast live coverage
of a seven-hour train ride --